metadata.name: Kitsune dream
metadata.description:
Her beauty will make you never wants to wake up from this dream. 
This fox girl, Kitsune, is an original character of Swheatz. His art is always full of details and vibrant red-purple color. I respect that style and invite her to my DAYDREAM collection. 
FYI, I spent most of the time drawing the kimono pattern all by myself. I'm quite proud of that.
